description.narrative: Enhanced support for disadvantaged and marginalized children and families to demand & use social protection systems and participate in decision-making processes affecting them (Social Protection Demand), which contributes to Social Protection, Social Protection And Child Poverty. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Adolescent girls and boys, mothers and fathers, and community leaders in 106 districts adopt 11 key life-saving, care and protective behaviours for children and women
